---
---

<section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
  <img
    src="/images/experience-bg.webp"
    alt="Palm trees on Kauai beach"
    class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/55"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 text-center">
    <p class="text-[var(--sage)] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">The Experience</p>
    <h2
      class="text-4xl md:text-6xl mb-6 leading-tight text-white"
      style="font-family: var(--font-serif)"
    >
      Where Island Paradise<br />
      Meets Deep Relaxation
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
      Imagine the gentle sound of waves, the warm Hawaiian sun, and skilled hands melting away every tension in your body.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      This isn't just a massage — it's an escape into pure tranquility. Whether you're celebrating an anniversary, honeymoon, or simply treating yourself, we create moments you'll treasure forever.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-10 text-white">
      <div>
        <p class="text-3xl mb-1" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">60-90min</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Session Options</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l border-white/20 pl-10">
        <p class="text-3xl mb-1" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">100%</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Customizable</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l border-white/20 pl-10">
        <p class="text-3xl mb-1" style="font-family: var(--font-serif)">Island-wide</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55">Mobile Service</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 z-10">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 99" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full">
      <path d="M0 30L60 40C120 50 240 70 360 75C480 80 600 70 720 60C840 50 960 40 1080 45C1200 50 1320 70 1380 80L1440 90V100H0V30Z" fill="#F5F0E9" fill-opacity="0.5"></path>
      <path d="M0 50L60 58C120 66 240 82 360 86C480 90 600 82 720 74C840 66 960 58 1080 62C1200 66 1320 82 1380 90L1440 98V100H0V50Z" fill="#F5F0E9"></path>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>
